{"tid":745833,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇野可以令人醒少少?","createTime":"2018-07-17T06:00:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T15:13:56.000Z","uid":126561,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2b09c64f4b5c50b1e2247243bdc59cc1f6a24430","tid":745833,"uid":126561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:00:17.000Z","msg":"成日覺得自己成個人好遲鈍<br />\n個腦好似塞住塞全<br />\n搞到做野又攰 又冇精神做<br />\n有冇D咩可以補下腦 令到個人做人醒少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw唔係咖啡果d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係真係supplement keep住食咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90d6ddd8c681756949917a4ffe675c3ef9627c3","tid":745833,"uid":126561,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0693e18702f878c1ed83a2771cacffe3a32405","tid":745833,"uid":90034,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:13:12.000Z","msg":"幫推, 日日都唔夠精神, 個人成日都好想訓"},{"pid":"eaa9f8f95455e96d9d39b684b9a2407e30c11837","tid":745833,"uid":75354,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:13:36.000Z","msg":"讀多啲書"},{"pid":"e7675446548ff8e8f4219fa9fbd2163540078c23","tid":745833,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:14:16.000Z","msg":"J少啲"},{"pid":"4edcfd483d9ab726b5a5fe939a452c70a7587b6e","tid":745833,"uid":92859,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T06:14:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/141424_59288208d8382c2e46a65bcfe0a49efc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F141424_59288208d8382c2e46a65bcfe0a49efc.png&h=22b6deec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b232c86ae85506d2a2a76c0760cd89410a8004f","tid":745833,"uid":171310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci